sequenceDiagram
actor User
participant WebBrowser
participant LoadBalancer
participant WebServer
participant ApplicationServer
participant Database
participant PaymentGateway
participant FinancialInstitution

User->>WebBrowser: Login request
WebBrowser->>LoadBalancer: HTTPS request
LoadBalancer->>WebServer: Routing
WebServer->>ApplicationServer: API call
ApplicationServer->>Database: Validate user
Database-->>ApplicationServer: User valid
ApplicationServer->>PaymentGateway: Charge card
PaymentGateway->>FinancialInstitution: Process payment
FinancialInstitution-->>PaymentGateway: Payment status
PaymentGateway-->>ApplicationServer: Payment result
ApplicationServer-->>WebServer: Payment response
WebServer-->>LoadBalancer: Response
LoadBalancer-->>WebBrowser: Response
WebBrowser-->>User: Payment result

User->>WebBrowser: Upload data file
WebBrowser->>LoadBalancer: HTTPS request
LoadBalancer->>WebServer: Routing
WebServer->>ApplicationServer: API call
ApplicationServer->>Database: Store data file
Database-->>ApplicationServer: Data file stored
ApplicationServer-->>WebServer: Success response
WebServer-->>LoadBalancer: Response
LoadBalancer-->>WebBrowser: Response
WebBrowser-->>User: Success message

User->>WebBrowser: Request dashboard analytics
WebBrowser->>LoadBalancer: HTTPS request
LoadBalancer->>WebServer: Routing
WebServer->>ApplicationServer: API call
ApplicationServer->>Database: Retrieve analytics data
Database-->>ApplicationServer: Analytics data
ApplicationServer-->>WebServer: Analytics response
WebServer-->>LoadBalancer: Response
LoadBalancer-->>WebBrowser: Response
WebBrowser-->>User: Dashboard analytics

User->>WebBrowser: Request predictive model training
WebBrowser->>LoadBalancer: HTTPS request
LoadBalancer->>WebServer: Routing
WebServer->>ApplicationServer: API call
ApplicationServer->>Database: Retrieve training data
Database-->>ApplicationServer: Training data
ApplicationServer->>ApplicationServer: Train predictive model
ApplicationServer-->>WebServer: Training result
WebServer-->>LoadBalancer: Response
LoadBalancer-->>WebBrowser: Response
WebBrowser-->>User: Training result

User->>WebBrowser: Request automated email notification
WebBrowser->>LoadBalancer: HTTPS request
LoadBalancer->>WebServer: Routing
WebServer->>ApplicationServer: API call
ApplicationServer->>Database: Retrieve notification settings
Database-->>ApplicationServer: Notification settings
ApplicationServer->>ApplicationServer: Send email notification
ApplicationServer-->>WebServer: Notification sent
WebServer-->>LoadBalancer: Response
LoadBalancer-->>WebBrowser: Response
WebBrowser-->>User: Notification sent